<div id='communityQuestionsWithAnswers'>
<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1121470-love-the-book-and-the-ideas-it-presents">Love the book and the ideas it presents, but not very impressed with the religion chapter-specifically in how it characterizes Jewish tradition. It seems she didn&#39;t research the tradition well enough to use it for a comparison. Her ideas about Niddah were pretty wrong and could have been amended by asking any knowledgeable Jewish person. Obviously this is not the point of the book but it was a detail that bothered me?</a>
</div>
